                  </hi>. I am counter clerk at the Western Branch of the Bank of England, Burlington Gardens—Rose brought me a cheque for 905<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. on 11th July, which 2 took to Mr. Farrel, the chief cashier—he sent it back.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18790915-name-126" type="witnessName">
